      <h4>Craft Brewing</h4>
      <p>I love that craft brewing has surged to the forefront of the American beer industry in recent years. I'm a huge proponent
        of small breweries. My current favorite is Eureka Heights in Houston, Texas. I like IPAs generaly, but also enjoy
        a nice stout or belgian quadrupel on occasion.</p>
